title: **Ibiza Live Mix Vol.3 Base Bar 2008**
description:
You know the score! Live all the way from the White Isles trendiest Bar. 4 complete sets of the Ibiza summer sound. DJ Mikael & Yoshi do the usual damage with some fantastic tunes & mixing. Base Bar resident DJ James Scott plays a blinder with his own style. Finally, flown in from Holland, Dries Van Hoorn with his electro house set. Dries is gaining a big reputation but, to be honest, I wasn&#039;t that impressed.

Party People let me know what you think and please, please SEED.
